											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "NodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "6 bespoke screams of growing intensity as each piece of the armor is destroyed.\r\n\r\nIntensity 1: light scream; character is still confident.\r\nIntensity 2: same as intensity 1, but with more anger and agitation\r\nIntensity 3: an angry mdium-intensity scream\r\nIntensity 4: same as intensity 3, but with pain mixed in\r\nIntensity 5: high intensity scream, almost like your arm got chopped off\r\nIntensity 6: highest possible intensity; character has no protection, no strength, nothing left - and is entering a state of desperation."
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "Quality"
