												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": " Feeling Stronger better, When an ally casts a helping spell on you, feeling more confident, protected, reassured. This will be cast on party members and only the enemies will cast it between themselves so we can really nail the feeling of Ah! “nothing can stop me now” a little laugh can really sell it (~1-2 sec)"
