												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "A fatigued/discouraged attack sound when the character is weak and enters the 'desperate' state. A high effort grunt but with a hint of pain in it and discouraged. You're attacking the player in your weakest state. You are scared and have no power. your strike is as strong as a wet noodle. "
